  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application\n\n1.1\n\nThis Part applies to every _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 19/06/2014*\n\n2\n\n###  Cooperation\n\n2.1\n\nThis Chapter does not apply to a _UK Solvency II firm_, the _Society_ or _managing agents_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n2.2\n\nA _firm_ must take reasonable steps to ensure that its agents, _appointed representatives_ and suppliers under _material outsourcing_ arrangements deal in an open, cooperative and timely way with the _PRA_ in the discharge of its functions under any _relevant legislation_ in relation to the _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n3\n\n###  Access to Premises\n\n3.1\n\n[3.3](/pra-rules/information-gathering#f1a9566d6a8a4197a604be616c201dfc \"3.3\") does not apply to a _UK Solvency II firm_ , the _Society_ or _managing agents_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n3.2\n\nA _firm_ must permit any representative or appointee of the _PRA_ to have access, with or without notice, during reasonable business hours to any of its business premises, in relation to the discharge of the _PRA’s_ functions under any _relevant legislation_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n3.3\n\nA _firm_ must take reasonable steps to ensure that its agents, _appointed representatives_ and suppliers under _material outsourcing_ arrangements permit any representative or appointee of the _PRA_ to have access, with or without notice, during reasonable business hours to any of its business premises, in relation to the discharge of the _PRA’s_ functions under any _relevant legislation_ in relation to the _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2016*\n\n4\n\n###  Access to Documents and Personnel\n\n4.1\n\nSubject to section 413 of _FSMA_ , a _firm_ must, in relation to the discharge of the _PRA’s_ functions under any _relevant legislation_ :\n\n  1. (1) permit any representative or appointee of the _PRA_ to have access to any document that the _PRA_ reasonably requests;\n  2. (2) make itself readily available to meet any representative or appointee of the _PRA_ as the _PRA_ reasonably requests; and\n  3. (3) answer truthfully, fully and promptly all questions reasonably put to it by any representative or appointee of the _PRA_.\n\n*Effective: 19/06/2014*\n\n4.2\n\nSubject to section 413 of _FSMA_ , a _firm_ must, in relation to the discharge of the _PRA’s_ functions under any _relevant legislation_ , take reasonable steps to ensure that the following _persons_ act in the manner set out in [4.1](/pra-rules/information-gathering#5382ee0ab9fe44f4bf4e2dc5edf7dfc8 \"4.1\") in relation to the _firm_ :\n\n  1. (1) its _employees_ , agents and _appointed representatives_ ; and\n  2. (2) any other members of its _group_ , and their _employees_ and agents.\n\n*Effective: 19/06/2014*\n\n5\n\n###  Information Requested on Behalf of Other Regulators\n\n5.1\n\nSubject to section 413 of _FSMA_ , a _firm_ must cooperate with the _PRA_ in providing information at the request of another regulator to enable that regulator to discharge its functions properly.\n\n*Effective: 19/06/2014*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"a50d11d1af1b47cbab82fbf4fc8470f4\" id=\"2c35e192785640278422544f1fb224a7\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9fe2d8a7567d43bdb76c587115e135d1\" id=\"b21a57f8c7044f6fbf786d4b8a3fa416\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Part applies to every <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t19/06/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"4a2d5ee03c8640d1bf8db01157415cf8\" id=\"098513af5a0b410e8fa003dbc7ac7fde\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tCooperation\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"889181814a924c1f8eebcbf46f19e886\" id=\"d2f77594a8244197a5e75189ec46ec1f\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This Chapter does not apply to a<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52930\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0d29d447fd4b4fca868c1d2e5b5e2276\" title=\"UK Solvency II firm\">UK Solvency II firm</a></em>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em> or <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52204\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-631b76adce9c4143ad8d33e593852c66\" title=\"managing agents\">managing agents</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/information-gathering/19-06-2014#d2f77594a8244197a5e75189ec46ec1f\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 2.1 before 01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"800202387deb4a85a67029808b537ae2\" id=\"f7a2f6f7c318401283e718b72cc0242b\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"15.620600000000003\">A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must take reasonable steps to ensure that its agents, <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52178\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cf60950dc57c44c098218161b24047e3\" title=\"appointed representatives\">appointed representatives</a></em> and suppliers under <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52175\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f8fd6084632547449e6472efbf6f4ffb\" title=\"material outsourcing\">material outsourcing</a></em> arrangements deal in an open, cooperative and timely way with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> in the discharge of its functions under any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52176\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-14493a5f658f421c8a27216e21bfd544\" title=\"relevant legislation\">relevant legislation</a></em> in relation to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"61f78e7b141a4049b4d4138e4f263f49\" id=\"c42b4cd7a95c49ac9c1beac81b50d638\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tAccess to Premises\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"d95db1c18a704fb09ad9309a8e9b1951\" id=\"feda642d4b2c4bce84ea8fff05469ef6\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p><a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/information-gathering#f1a9566d6a8a4197a604be616c201dfc\" title=\"3.3\">3.3</a> does not apply to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52930\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0d29d447fd4b4fca868c1d2e5b5e2276\" title=\"UK Solvency II firm\">UK Solvency II firm</a></em>, the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52231\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c757d61ac22a4f43b4565c1a14c53dfd\" title=\"Society\">Society</a></em> or <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52204\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-631b76adce9c4143ad8d33e593852c66\" title=\"managing agents\">managing agents</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/information-gathering/19-06-2014#feda642d4b2c4bce84ea8fff05469ef6\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.1 before 01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"3d44503e625244f5888f009ea4e76f25\" id=\"db1fc17195c646a482cacd246e8c8d8c\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"15.620600000000003\">A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must permit any representative or appointee of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> to have access, with or without notice, during reasonable business hours to any of its business premises, in relation to the discharge of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA’s\">PRA’s</a></em> functions under any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52176\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-14493a5f658f421c8a27216e21bfd544\" title=\"relevant legislation\">relevant legislation</a></em>.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/information-gathering/19-06-2014#db1fc17195c646a482cacd246e8c8d8c\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.2 before 01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"ec994c0753ed4788b227675b4af94595\" id=\"f1a9566d6a8a4197a604be616c201dfc\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"15.620600000000003\">A<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must take reasonable steps to ensure that its agents, <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52178\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cf60950dc57c44c098218161b24047e3\" title=\"appointed representatives\">appointed representatives</a></em> and suppliers under <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52175\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f8fd6084632547449e6472efbf6f4ffb\" title=\"material outsourcing\">material outsourcing</a></em> arrangements permit any representative or appointee of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> to have access, with or without notice, during reasonable business hours to any of its business premises, in relation to the discharge of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA’s\">PRA’s</a></em> functions under any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52176\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-14493a5f658f421c8a27216e21bfd544\" title=\"relevant legislation\">relevant legislation</a></em> in relation to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2016\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"bcc0493ce9b247f38c41952b231f389c\" id=\"ea623ece5c514fdd93c6e5d5f53d2fbf\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tAccess to Documents and Personnel\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"5d360cdde55e47d88124c96f3999f9aa\" id=\"5382ee0ab9fe44f4bf4e2dc5edf7dfc8\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"187.1484\">Subject to section 413 of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must, in relation to the discharge of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA’s</a></em> functions under any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52176\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-14493a5f658f421c8a27216e21bfd544\" title=\"relevant legislation\">relevant legislation</a></em>:</div>\n<div data-canvas-width=\"20.2852\"><ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) permit any representative or appointee of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> to have access to any document that the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> reasonably requests;</li>\n<li>(2) make itself readily available to meet any representative or appointee of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> as the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> reasonably requests; and</li>\n<li>(3) answer truthfully, fully and promptly all questions reasonably put to it by any representative or appointee of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>.</li>\n</ol></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t19/06/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"52721e17c827430d98b5b0ff22bee880\" id=\"b5f9655f9f0447a99e28a29a1f0be318\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"187.1484\">Subject to section 413 of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must, in relation to the discharge of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA’s\">PRA’s</a></em> functions under any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52176\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-14493a5f658f421c8a27216e21bfd544\" title=\"relevant legislation\">relevant legislation</a></em>, take reasonable steps to ensure that the following <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52181\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-08c2a4c6b87b4e51a4292e13ba411052\" title=\"persons\">persons</a></em> act in the manner set out in <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/information-gathering#5382ee0ab9fe44f4bf4e2dc5edf7dfc8\" title=\"4.1\">4.1</a> in relation to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>:</div>\n<div data-canvas-width=\"20.2852\"><ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\">(1) its </span><em style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52174\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e08f83ef44794a06bd2429270dc7b807\" title=\"employees\">employees</a></em><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\">, agents and </span><em style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52178\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-cf60950dc57c44c098218161b24047e3\" title=\"appointed representatives\">appointed representatives</a></em><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\">; and</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\">(2) any other members of its </span><em style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52429\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-863f3d175b7a4e4aac87107d310dec2a\" title=\"group\">group</a></em><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\">, and their </span><em style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\"><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52174\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-e08f83ef44794a06bd2429270dc7b807\" title=\"employees\">employees</a></em><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: -1.3em;\"> and agents.</span></li>\n</ol></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t19/06/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"af3c6fcfaa8746518054366c938dc1f0\" id=\"c4cda97c0ee64ee49ac5aec3ff452ae2\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t5\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tInformation Requested on Behalf of Other Regulators\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"bf854f5c84bd4236bad35828a318e0a5\" id=\"6833015ed73d461faf644bde6910d98e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"187.1484\">Subject to section 413 of <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52115\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-d7aa340192de4d37b63a54ba1489ac08\" title=\"FSMA\">FSMA</a></em>, a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must cooperate with the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> in providing information at the request of another regulator to enable that regulator to discharge its functions properly.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t19/06/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
